<span id="freeTextContainer7436917205954913265"><br/>Wonderful - it may have been four stars were it not for the accompanying illustrations, which in my edition are by Ron Wegan. The combination of the words with the illustrations, which are as valuable in adding punctuation, depth and breathing space as they are in their beauty, make this book something special for me. <br/><br/>It&apos;s a small book, and I found my copy for 49p in a charity shop; a hidden gem that I stumbled across just when I really needed to.</span>
  <span id="freeText7436917205954913265" style="display:none"><br />Wonderful - it may have been four stars were it not for the accompanying illustrations, which in my edition are by Ron Wegan. The combination of the words with the illustrations, which are as valuable in adding punctuation, depth and breathing space as they are in their beauty, make this book something special for me. <br /><br />It's a small book, and I found my copy for 49p in a charity shop; a hidden gem that I stumbled across just when I really needed to.</span>
