<span id="freeTextContainer9593141661048020513">There&apos;s something in here about friendship and being, but its metaphysical meaning failed to penetrate my cynical armour. Nice illustrations though.</span>
  <span id="freeText9593141661048020513" style="display:none">There's something in here about friendship and being, but its metaphysical meaning failed to penetrate my cynical armour. Nice illustrations though.</span>
